#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat >&2 <<'EOF'
hapax-gemini-send is retired.

There is no supported legacy hapax-gemini tmux lane to send prompts to. Use
hapax-gemini-sidecar for read-only packet work, or agy.review.direct through
scripts/hapax-agy-reviewer for admitted review-plane work.
EOF
